A lone figure in traditional meditation robes sits in perfect stillness atop a floating rock fragment, suspended in the vast expanse of a swirling cosmic nebula. Studio Ghibli style with soft, dreamy watercolor textures and luminous colors. The meditating person is small against the immense backdrop of spiraling galaxies, glowing purple and gold stardust, and distant celestial bodies. Wispy clouds drift between stars, creating a sense of peaceful infinity. The figure's silhouette is serene, connected to everything around them—their robes gently flowing as if breathing with the universe itself. Warm amber light emanates from their center, blending seamlessly into the cool blues and violets of deep space. Delicate shooting stars trace gentle arcs across the scene. The composition evokes profound unity between the individual and the infinite cosmos, stillness within boundless motion.
